# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:12
translate portuguese suzy0_b52dca5a:

    # "I go to the kitchen and make a plate with what's left, then sit down across from her at the table."
    "Vou à cozinha e preparo um prato com o que sobrou, depois sento-me à mesa, à frente dela."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:13
translate portuguese suzy0_a9d96a39:

    # "She doesn't even look up at me as she casually eats, not really even paying attention to the fact that I'm there."
    "Ela nem sequer olha para mim enquanto come casualmente, sem prestar realmente atenção ao facto de eu estar ali."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:16
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_752743ef:

    # pc "So how have you been doing?"
    pc "Então, como tens passado?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:18
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_7a0e54f8:

    # "She raises her eyes towards me, looking slightly annoyed by my question."
    "Ela levanta os olhos para mim, parecendo ligeiramente irritada com a minha pergunta."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:19
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_19dcc455:

    # ss "I've been fine."
    ss "Tenho estado bem."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:20
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_ed75df6c:

    # pc "School going okay?"
    pc "A escola está a correr bem?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:21
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_95991dd2:

    # ss "We've barely started the semester. I don't know how it's going."
    ss "Mal começámos o semestre. Não sei como está a correr."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:22
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_6150338d:

    # pc "And work? You work at Java Lava, right?"
    pc "E o trabalho? Trabalhas no Java Lava, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:24
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_13de2504:

    # "She turns her phone off and slides it into her pocket, then really looks up at me for the first time."
    "Ela desliga o telemóvel e enfia-o no bolso, depois olha realmente para mim pela primeira vez."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:25
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_ae5be968:

    # ss "Yeah. It's fine. It's not too hard and I get paid."
    ss "Sim. Está tudo bem. Não é muito difícil e recebo o meu salário."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:29
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_e05d2344:

    # ss "Oh man, you wouldn't believe the guys we get in there."
    ss "Caramba, nem acreditas no tipo de gente que aparece por lá."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:30
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_322cf28b:

    # pc "Who's your weirdest."
    pc "Quem é o mais esquisito?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:31
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_cd997a04:

    # ss "So there was this one guy who comes in all the time. I don't even remember his name; we just call him kombucha guy."
    ss "Bem, há um tipo que aparece lá constantemente. Nem me lembro do nome dele; chamamos-lhe simplesmente «o tipo do kombucha»."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:32
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_be9a8d1f:

    # ss "We serve kombucha tea there, but it rarely gets ordered. But this guy comes in almost every day, at least four times a week, and buys two kombucha teas."
    ss "Servimos chá de kombucha lá, mas raramente é pedido. Mas este tipo aparece quase todos os dias, pelo menos quatro vezes por semana, e compra dois chás de kombucha."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:33
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_23ceb711:

    # ss "He sits at a table by himself and stares out the window and drinks both of those teas back to back, then leaves a two-dollar tip and leaves."
    ss "Senta-se sozinho numa mesa, fica a olhar pela janela e bebe os dois chás seguidos, depois deixa uma gorjeta de dois dólares e vai-se embora."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:34
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_f53e358e:

    # pc "Weird. Have you ever talked to him?"
    pc "Estranho. Já falaste com ele?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:35
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_0ef624f4:

    # ss "Oh yeah. He's a little crazy. He says that he's some kind of musician and he tried to get Tammy to go out with him. He told her that he's really famous over in Japan."
    ss "Ah, sim. Ele é um pouco maluco. Diz que é uma espécie de músico e tentou convencer a Tammy a sair com ele. Disse-lhe que é muito famoso no Japão."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:36
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_d22ad849:

    # ss "Then he went on and on about how Japan is way better than here. How they have holographic baristas that make your coffee and bring it to your table."
    ss "Depois, ele não parava de falar sobre como o Japão é muito melhor do que aqui. Como lá têm baristas holográficos que preparam o café e o levam até à mesa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:37
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_fa3e4e10:

    # ss "How he bought a phone there five years ago for $20 and doesn't have to pay a monthly fee because it runs off a satellite."
    ss "Como comprou um telemóvel lá há cinco anos por 20 dólares e não tem de pagar nenhuma mensalidade porque funciona via satélite."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:38
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_ce59dba2:

    # pc "Wow."
    pc "Uau."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:39
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_faaa2ecb:

    # ss "He's always hitting on Tammy every time he comes in. She likes to mess with him too."
    ss "Ele está sempre a dar em cima da Tammy sempre que entra. Ela também gosta de brincar com ele."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:40
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_9e19cf64:

    # ss "He came in one time and was telling her about how he invented this new clock that was small, and you could carry it around with you."
    ss "Uma vez ele entrou e estava a contar-lhe que tinha inventado um relógio novo que era pequeno e que se podia levar para todo o lado."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:41
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_5d1c5ae8:

    # pc "Isn't that just a watch?"
    pc "Isso não é apenas um relógio de pulso?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:42
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c152b77b:

    # ss "That's what Tammy said. He argued with her and told her it was completely different."
    ss "Foi o que a Tammy disse. Ele discutiu com ela e disse-lhe que era completamente diferente."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:43
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_3791927f:

    # ss "So the next day she told him about how she had invented this new type of pastries that had fruit filling and were sold in individual packages and would fit perfectly in your toaster."
    ss "Então, no dia seguinte, ela contou-lhe que tinha inventado um novo tipo de pastéis com recheio de fruta, vendidos em embalagens individuais e que cabiam perfeitamente na torradeira."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:44
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_74618d28:

    # pc "Pop Tarts?"
    pc "Pop Tarts?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:45
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c72adb9b:

    # ss "Yeah, but he'd apparently never heard of them, because he went on and on about how it was an amazing idea and how he wanted to pay her to buy that idea from her so he could make it."
    ss "Sim, mas aparentemente ele nunca tinha ouvido falar delas, porque não parava de dizer que era uma ideia fantástica e que queria pagar-lhe para lhe comprar a ideia, para poder produzi-las."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:46
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_e8b6bb21:

    # pc "Did she take his money?"
    pc "Ela aceitou o dinheiro dele?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:47
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_75e09394:

    # ss "Fifty bucks."
    ss "Cinquenta dólares."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:48
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_5cbde015:

    # pc "That's fucked up!"
    pc "Isso é de doido!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:50
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_5f99478a:

    # ss "I know right?"
    ss "Eu sei, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:51
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c085fd14:

    # "She starts laughing, and I can't help but to laugh too."
    "Ela começa a rir, e eu não consigo evitar rir também."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:55
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_74c7877c:

    # ss "Yeah, I don't do that stuff. I kind of feel bad for him."
    ss "Sim, eu não faço esse tipo de coisa. Sinto um pouco de pena dele."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:56
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_d31a7dfa:

    # ss "He seems like he's not playing with a full deck, you know? I figure he's probably had a rough life."
    ss "Ele parece não ter todas as tachas no lugar, percebes? Acho que ele provavelmente teve uma vida difícil."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:57
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_9ccec7b2:

    # ss "But Tammy is just like that."
    ss "Mas a Tammy é assim mesmo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:58
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_e0586b57:

    # ss "She can take care of herself though. She does MMA, you know? Fights in a ring and everything."
    ss "Mas ela sabe cuidar de si. Ela pratica MMA, sabes? Luta no ringue e tudo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:59
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_399bdc0f:

    # pc "Really?"
    pc "A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:60
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_02b90fe6:

    # ss "Yeah. She's good too. I've gone and watched her fight before. She can seriously kick some ass."
    ss "Sim. Ela é boa também. Já fui ver-lhe lutar antes. Ela consegue mesmo dar porrada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:61
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_1189f258:

    # pc "You never wanted to get into it though?"
    pc "Mas nunca quiseste entrar nisso?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:62
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_a7e15ac4:

    # ss "Nah. It's too much work for me, and I really don't want to get hit."
    ss "Não. É demasiado trabalho para mim, e não quero mesmo levar porrada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:65
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_9f26e184:

    # ss "Aw, thanks, [bro]. I'm glad you don't want me to get beat up."
    ss "Ah, obrigado, [bro]. Fico contente por não quereres que eu leve porrada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:66
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_3090c620:

    # pc "If I saw somebody hitting you, even in a ring, even if it was a girl, I'd have to kick their ass. It's in the big [brother] rulebook."
    pc "Se visse alguém a bater-te, mesmo num ringue, mesmo que fosse uma rapariga, teria de lhes dar uma sova. Está no grande [brother] livro de regras."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:68
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_caad0343:

    # "She burst into laughter."
    "Ela desatou a rir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:69
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_0cfa18a1:

    # ss "I don't think you could even take these girls. Tammy would wipe the floor with you."
    ss "Acho que nem sequer conseguias dar conta destas raparigas. A Tammy ia dar-te uma sova de fazer asperas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:70
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "Ah, sim?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:72
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_4122a41e:

    # ss "Yeah, definitely."
    ss "Sim, sem dúvida."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:73
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_2d87f285:

    # pc "Well I'd get my ass kicked so you didn't have to then."
    pc "Bem, então eu levava uma sova para que tu não tivesses de levar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:74
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_906493b5:

    # ss "Really? You'd get your ass kicked for me?"
    ss "A sério? Levarias uma sova por mim?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:77
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_d120684f:

    # ss "I don't believe you."
    ss "Não acredito em ti."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:79
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_9f7e6e8a:

    # ss "See, I knew it!"
    ss "Vês, eu sabia!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:82
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_934dd153:

    # ss "Anger? What anger? I'm not angry at anybody."
    ss "Raiva? Que raiva? Não estou zangado com ninguém."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:83
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_b287d4be:

    # pc "You seem angry at me."
    pc "Pareces zangado comigo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:84
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_87014878:

    # ss "Well, if you were in the ring with me, yeah, I could channel that anger into an ass kicking."
    ss "Bem, se estivesses no ringue comigo, sim, poderia canalizar essa raiva para te dar uma sova."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:85
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_e7037ffa:

    # pc "I don't know. I think I could take you."
    pc "Não sei. Acho que te daria conta."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:87
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_a43ee1a8:

    # ss "Not as often as they do Tammy, but I get one or two a day."
    ss "Não com tanta frequência como com a Tammy, mas recebo uma ou duas por dia."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:88
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_046a9753:

    # ss "I've gone on dates with a few of the guys that I've met there, but nothing really panned out."
    ss "Já saí com alguns dos tipos que conheci lá, mas nada deu em nada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:89
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_b102ceb1:

    # pc "Nobody harassing you though?"
    pc "Mas ninguém te assedia?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:90
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_f72e097b:

    # ss "Nah, not really."
    ss "Não, nem por isso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:91
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_0ac94505:

    # pc "Good. I'd hate to have to bust some heads."
    pc "Ótimo. Detestaria ter de partir algumas cabeças."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:93
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_35df88eb:

    # ss "Bust heads? You? Don't make me laugh."
    ss "Partir cabeças? Tu? Não me faças rir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:94
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_4d303faa:

    # pc "Hey! I could do it."
    pc "Ei! Eu era capaz."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:98
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_a79bfefa:

    # ss "Really? You're going to ask me how much I make. That's none of your damn business."
    ss "A sério? Vais perguntar-me quanto ganho. Isso não te diz nada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:99
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_02a4aa53:

    # pc "Sorry, I was just making conversation."
    pc "Desculpa, estava só a puxar conversa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:101
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_e2bc9fa0:

    # ss "Well, make it with somebody else. I'm not interested in talking to you."
    ss "Bem, vai puxar conversa com outra pessoa. Não estou interessada em falar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:102
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_b57d2eab:

    # "Before I can apologize, she stands up and walks out of the room."
    "Antes que eu consiga pedir desculpa, ela levanta-se e sai da sala."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:103
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_d8f00519:

    # "I guess I'll have to try to fix things with her some other day."
    "Acho que vou ter de tentar resolver as coisas com ela noutro dia."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:104
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c0aeac6d:

    # "I finish eating by myself and then clean off the table and get ready to go to school."
    "Termino de comer sozinho, limpo a mesa e preparo-me para ir para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:108
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_1b55d4a6:

    # ss "That doesn't really surprise me. You would suck at it."
    ss "Isso não me surpreende. Serias péssimo nisso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:109
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_142311fd:

    # ss "You're not good at talking to people. You just whine and get on everybody's nerves."
    ss "Não és bom a falar com as pessoas. Só te queixas e irritas toda a gente."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:112
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_d1097009:

    # ss "I think you whine too much and pity yourself, yes."
    ss "Acho que te queixas demais e tens pena de ti mesmo, sim."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:113
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_a8b0992c:

    # pc "I'm really not like that though. You don't really even know me."
    pc "Mas eu não sou assim. Nem me conheces."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:115
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_952b2153:

    # ss "Sure you are. You whine and you pity yourself."
    ss "Claro que és. Tu queixas-te e tens pena de ti próprio."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:116
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_fbb5736d:

    # pc "You don't really even know me."
    pc "Tu nem me conheces a sério."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:118
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_db9ad157:

    # ss "Better than you. All you do is whine and pity yourself."
    ss "Melhor do que tu. Tudo o que fazes é queixar-te e ter pena de ti próprio."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:119
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c4de7a83:

    # pc "What are you talking about. You barely even know me."
    pc "Do que é que estás a falar? Tu mal me conheces."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:120
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_9965969f:

    # ss "You never gave me the chance to get to know you. When we started getting used to each other and getting along, you just up and left."
    ss "Nunca me deste a oportunidade de te conhecer. Quando começámos a habituar-nos um ao outro e a dar-nos bem, tu simplesmente levantaste-te e foste-te embora."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:121
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_9ef2ee78:

    # pc "I'm not going to leave this time. I'm going to stay here and help out."
    pc "Desta vez não vou embora. Vou ficar aqui e ajudar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:124
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c0dc7bfc:

    # ss "I don't see how that's any of your business, but yes. His name is Tim and he lives in Whiterock."
    ss "Não vejo como isso te diz respeito, mas sim. O nome dele é Tim e ele mora em Whiterock."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:125
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_130cbb47:

    # pc "How's the long-distance thing working out?"
    pc "Como está a correr essa coisa de longa distância?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:127
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_2c9e2c8d:

    # ss "I'm not going to talk to you about my relationships."
    ss "Não vou falar contigo sobre os meus relacionamentos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:128
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_1422ef63:

    # pc "Why not? What's a big [brother] for, if not for giving advice?"
    pc "Por que não? Para que serve um grande [brother], se não for para dar conselhos?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:129
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_372edb07:

    # ss "In my experience, a big [brother] is only there to be annoying and then abandon you."
    ss "Pela minha experiência, um grande [brother] só existe para ser irritante e depois abandonar-te."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:130
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_620cccdd:

    # pc "I didn't abandon you Suzy. I went to college."
    pc "Eu não te abandonei, Suzy. Fui para a faculdade."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:131
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_43e8a5ea:

    # ss "Same difference. You could have written or called or something."
    ss "É a mesma coisa. Podias ter escrito, ligado ou algo assim."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:132
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_cdfa161d:

    # pc "Well I'm here now. I'm not going to leave again. I'm going to stay and help."
    pc "Bem, agora estou aqui. Não vou embora de novo. Vou ficar e ajudar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:135
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_db8d354f:

    # ss "I have no idea. Rumor is that he found another woman and disappeared with her."
    ss "Não faço ideia. Dizem que ele encontrou outra mulher e desapareceu com ela."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:136
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_4183655a:

    # pc "Where are you hearing these rumors?"
    pc "Onde estás a ouvir esses rumores?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:137
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_6f70f528:

    # ss "Just around town."
    ss "Por aí na cidade."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:138
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_adc582ed:

    # pc "Do you think there's any truth to it? Did you ever see him with anybody?"
    pc "Achas que há alguma verdade nisso? Alguma vez o viste com alguém?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:140
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_c058de0d:

    # ss "He was so secretive about everything. He stayed in the basement all the time and barely talked to us in the weeks before he disappeared."
    ss "Ele era tão reservado em relação a tudo. Ficava na cave o tempo todo e mal falava connosco nas semanas antes de desaparecer."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:141
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_0c233c3e:

    # ss "So no, I never saw him with anybody, because I barely saw him at all."
    ss "Então, não, nunca o vi com ninguém, porque mal o via."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:143
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_b8c6a91b:

    # ss "I don't know if he left with somebody else, but I wouldn't be surprised. I mean, what else could it be?"
    ss "Não sei se ele partiu com outra pessoa, mas não ficaria surpreendida. Quer dizer, o que mais poderia ser?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:144
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_584eeb38:

    # pc "I'm sorry that you had to deal with this all alone."
    pc "Lamento que tenhas tido de lidar com isto sozinha."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:145
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_61d6e76f:

    # pc "But I'm here to help now."
    pc "Mas agora estou aqui para ajudar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:149
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_fcfa5eb9:

    # ss "Are you fucking serious?"
    ss "Estás a falar a sério?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:150
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_448a6b89:

    # ss "It's my bathroom. Not your bathroom. Not our bathroom. MY bathroom!"
    ss "É a minha casa de banho. Não é a tua casa de banho. Não é a nossa casa de banho. É a MINHA casa de banho!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:151
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_558e1795:

    # ss "If you don't like it, you can just get the fuck out."
    ss "Se não gostas, podes ir-te lixar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:152
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_e861901c:

    # pc "We're going to have to learn to share."
    pc "Vamos ter de aprender a partilhar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:153
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_5b696ff4:

    # ss "No we're not. You're going to have to learn that it's my space and you can go fuck yourself."
    ss "Não, não vamos. Vais ter de aprender que este é o meu espaço e que podes ir-te foder."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:154
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_2c586b30:

    # pc "What's the use of us being mad at each other all the time?"
    pc "De que adianta estarmos sempre zangados um com o outro?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:155
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_86802cd2:

    # ss "Leave me alone. I don't want to talk to you, I'm just trying to eat breakfast here."
    ss "Deixa-me em paz. Não quero falar contigo, só estou a tentar tomar o pequeno-almoço."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:156
translate portuguese breakfastmenu_15190116:

    # pc "Fine."
    pc "Tudo bem."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:163
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_a9b7d881:

    # ss "You talk a big game, but when it comes down to it, you'll run away."
    ss "Falas muito, mas quando chega a hora da verdade, fugas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:164
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_e9414b02:

    # ss "Just like you ran away to Brazil."
    ss "Tal como fugiste para o Brasil."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:165
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_5d857346:

    # pc "I didn't run away. I got a scholarship. It was the best college for my field."
    pc "Eu não fugi. Consegui uma bolsa de estudo. Era a melhor faculdade para a minha área."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:166
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_e67211ab:

    # ss "We were just starting to get along. I was actually starting to enjoy having you around. My big [brother]."
    ss "Estávamos a começar a dar-nos bem. Eu estava mesmo a começar a gostar de te ter por perto. O meu grande [brother]."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:167
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_1ddfbed6:

    # ss "Then you just leave and don't even call me, e-mail me, nothing."
    ss "Depois, simplesmente fugas e nem sequer me ligas, mandas um e-mail, nada."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:168
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_6e56d9fd:

    # ss "You just leave. It felt like you wanted to get as far away from us as possible."
    ss "Simplesmente fugas. Parecia que querias afastar-te o mais possível de nós."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:169
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_65a60962:

    # pc "That wasn't it."
    pc "Não foi isso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:171
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_304ad7a9:

    # ss "Don't lie. I can tell when you're lying."
    ss "Não mintas. Eu consigo perceber quando estás a mentir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:172
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_63428b62:

    # pc "Okay, maybe I did want to get away a bit. But it wasn't about you or Lisa. It was just that I missed my mom and didn't like to see her replaced."
    pc "Está bem, talvez eu quisesse afastar-me um pouco. Mas não tinha nada a ver contigo ou com a Lisa. Era só que sentia saudades da minha mãe e não gostava de a ver substituída."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:173
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_238de080:

    # pc "I see now that I was childish then. That you weren't replacing her."
    pc "Agora percebo que fui infantil naquela altura. Que tu não a estavas a substituir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:174
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_e4ed90e5:

    # pc "I'm sorry. I'll do better now."
    pc "Desculpa. Vou portar-me melhor agora."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:175
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_6e67a0a4:

    # pc "I want us to be friends."
    pc "Quero que sejamos amigas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:177
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_9a7d3359:

    # pc "I care about you Suzy. I really do."
    pc "Gosto de ti, Suzy. A sério."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:178
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_bf55225d:

    # ss "I care about you too, I guess."
    ss "Também gosto de ti, acho eu."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:179
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_02d6656a:

    # pc "So can we put all that junk behind us."
    pc "Então, podemos deixar toda aquela treta para trás?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:180
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_0ad83f38:

    # ss "Yeah. Let's do that. Let's start over."
    ss "Sim. Vamos fazer isso. Vamos recomeçar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:181
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_af3bb346:

    # pc "Great. Love you, [sis]. Glad we had this talk."
    pc "Ótimo. Adoro-te, [sis]. Ainda bem que tivemos esta conversa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:182
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_9e6f116f:

    # ss "Do you want to hug or something?"
    ss "Queres dar um abraço ou algo do género?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:183
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_67aa3ee7:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do that."
    pc "Sim, vamos fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:186
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_c6b79ddd:

    # "We stand up and walk over towards each other. It is awkward at first, but after I wrap my arms around her and pull her close, we both relax."
    "Levantamo-nos e caminhamos um em direção ao outro. É estranho no início, mas depois de a abraçar e puxá-la para perto de mim, ambos relaxamos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:187
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_e43a87e0:

    # "It feels right. I really do care about her and I feel like we can have a real relationship now."
    "Parece certo. Preocupo-me mesmo com ela e sinto que agora podemos ter uma relação a sério."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:188
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_710152a6:

    # ss "I love you too [bro]. I'm glad you're back home."
    ss "Também te adoro, [bro]. Ainda bem que voltaste para casa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:190
translate portuguese suzyreconcile_7264edb7:

    # "With that, it's time to go to school, so we say our goodbyes and I head out."
    "Dito isto, está na hora de ir para a escola, por isso despedimo-nos e eu saio."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:194
translate portuguese suzynoreconcile_68750ffa:

    # "We sit in silence until eventually Suzy gets up and stomps away upstairs."
    "Ficamos sentados em silêncio até que, por fim, a Suzy se levanta e sobe as escadas a dar passos pesados."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:196
translate portuguese suzynoreconcile_b9fe82ed:

    # "This hadn't gone as well as I'd hoped. I guess I'll have to try to talk to her some other time."
    "Isto não correu tão bem como eu esperava. Acho que vou ter de tentar falar com ela noutra altura."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:197
translate portuguese suzynoreconcile_db1e9d34:

    # "Right now though, it's time for school, so I clean up my dishes and head out."
    "Mas, neste momento, é hora de ir para a escola, por isso lavo a louça e saio."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:2
    old "Suzy eats breakfast in the dining room every weekday morning before school."
    new "A Suzy toma o pequeno-almoço na sala de jantar todas as manhãs da semana antes da escola."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:3
    old "You could try to have breakfast with her. Remember to be nice."
    new "Podes tentar tomar o pequeno-almoço com ela. Lembra-te de ser simpático."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:15
    old "How have you been?"
    new "Como tens passado?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:27
    old "You ever get any weird customers?"
    new "Já tiveste algum cliente esquisito?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:53
    old "You should be careful messing with people like that."
    new "Devias ter cuidado ao meter-te com pessoas assim."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:64
    old "Yeah, I wouldn't like to see you getting hit either."
    new "Sim, também não gostaria de te ver a levar porrada."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:76
    old "Of course."
    new "Claro."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:80
    old "You'd probably be good at it; you could put that anger to use."
    new "Provavelmente serias boa nisso; podias aproveitar essa raiva."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:86
    old "Do guys ever hit on you too?"
    new "Os rapazes também te atiram?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:96
    old "How much does it pay?"
    new "Quanto é que pagam?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:107
    old "I think I'd hate it."
    new "Acho que iria detestar."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:111
    old "You really think that about me?"
    new "Achas mesmo isso de mim?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:114
    old "I'm not like that."
    new "Eu não sou assim."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:117
    old "You think that you're good at talking to people?"
    new "Achas que és boa a falar com as pessoas?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:123
    old "You have a boyfriend?"
    new "Tens namorado?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:134
    old "Do you know anything about what happened to dad?"
    new "Sabes alguma coisa sobre o que aconteceu ao pai?"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:147
    old "You should clean your mess in the bathroom."
    new "Devias limpar a tua confusão na casa de banho."

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy0.rpy:158
    old "Stay quiet and leave her alone."
    new "Fica calado e deixa-a em paz."

